window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Are you thinking of launching your own web-based startup? Do you have an idea for a website or company you want to bring to life? In <i>Web-Based Startups: 21 Things Every Entrepreneur Needs to Know About Web Design and Internet Marketing</i>, Paul J. Scott shares what he’s learned about establishing and growing brand new businesses.&nbsp;</p> <p>Drawing on his experience as a web designer, marketing consultant, and successful entrepreneur, he breaks key web startup concepts into easy-to-use tips and advice. Whether you’re looking to revolutionize an industry or just change your own life, this is the one book you need before launching your online business.</p>"; 
